<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="arm-n">arm <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɑːm/    美 /ɑːrm/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>手臂；胳膊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>hold / take sb in one’s arms</strong>
将某人抱在怀中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He caught the thief <strong>by the arm</strong>. 
他抓住了小偷的胳膊。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(椅子的) 扶手</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[正式用语] [复数] 武器：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The soldiers <strong>took up arms</strong> to fight.
士兵们拿起武器战斗。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="arm-in-arm">arm in arm</h3>
<p>1.<strong>臂挽臂地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They walked along the beach arm in arm. 
他们臂挽臂沿着沙滩散步。</p></div>

<h3 id="with-open-arms">with open arms</h3>
<p>1.<strong>热烈地；热情地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are sure to welcome you with open arms.
他们肯定会热情地欢迎你。</p></div></div>